data.title: 76ers President Daryl Morey proves that sometimes, the best deals are the ones that aren't made
data.meta_description: Morey has made some missteps since taking the reins in 2020, but the Sharon Township native's finest actions have been moments of inaction. There have been three of them, and we're on the cusp of his latest demonstration of discipline, in this, his greatest hour of need.
